@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}
<div class="container mt-5">
    <h2 class="text-center mb-4">About Us</h2>
    <p class="lead text-center mb-4">
        At ABC Retail, we are committed to transforming the retail landscape by providing innovative technology solutions tailored for online retailers.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
        Our focus is on helping rapidly growing companies like ourselves, which face significant challenges due to outdated infrastructure and inefficient data management systems.
    </p>
    <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Our Current Challenges</h5>
            <p class="card-text">
                Currently, we operate an order processing system reliant on an aging on-premises infrastructure, which struggles to handle increased transaction volumes during peak seasons like the Christmas Holidays. Our existing relational database system often leads to delays, customer complaints, and missed sales opportunities. We understand that these operational inefficiencies hinder growth and customer satisfaction.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Inefficiencies in Operations</h5>
            <p class="card-text">
                Additionally, our reliance on network shared drives for storing product images creates storage inefficiencies and slow access times. The outdated message queuing system, supported by legacy middleware, lacks scalability and reliability, resulting in delays and processing errors. Our mission is to implement robust, scalable solutions that optimize order processing and enhance message delivery, addressing these critical issues.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Our Vision</h5>
            <p class="card-text">
                Even with our migration to cloud services, we continue to encounter obstacles in real-time event processing and reliable messaging. We specialize in developing customized solutions that integrate seamlessly with existing systems, ensuring scalability and flexibility to meet our growing business demands. Our advanced data analytics infrastructure empowers us to efficiently process diverse data types, generate actionable insights, and personalize customer experiences.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <h4 class="text-center mt-4">Join Us</h4>
    <p class="text-center">
        Partner with us to navigate the complexities of the retail environment. Together, we can enhance operational efficiency, optimize product recommendations, and drive sustainable growth in our business. Let’s redefine success in retail through innovation and technology.
    </p>
</div>
